commit.message:
Fixes ExtrudedChoroplethLayer attribute updates and defaults (#244)

* Fixes ExtrudedChoroplethLayer attribute updates and defaults

* Add Scatterplot fixes
Update CHANGELOG
Update React prop types (#237)
Build on Node 6 & 7 (#242)
Rebased to master
Merge branch 'reflection' of https://github.com/person594/deck.gl into person594-reflection

Line layer elevations (#241)

* Add elevations to LineLayer and LineLayer64

* test log

* test again

* Fix fp64 elevations. Add basic FPS stats widget

* Address apercu feedback

Minor correction and wording improvements in line and arc layer documentation. (#235)

Thanks again @tehwalris - merged to master. Text will be updated on github pages next time we publish our demo.

Make shaders customizable. Scatterplot32 instanceRadius, fixes #238. (#240)

* Make shaders customizable. Scatterplot32 instanceRadius, fixes #238.

* Fix travis tests

Effects are now loaded from the react component, like we do for layers
Currently they are not enabled for any components in the demo pages, as they are still experimental
added tests for experimental effect stuff
Add dist-demo to .gitattributes

Replace glslify with brfs (#236)

* Replace glslify with brfs

Improve DX by enabling hot reload of vertex and fragments shaders.
Ease usage outside of Browserify.

Related to #231.

* Merge imports & order, unify enhanced choropleth
added a bunch of comments
moved all code dealing with effects to src/experimental
replaced references to deckgl in effects and in the effectmanager with a reference to the layermanager
plz travis
additional sacrifices to the travis-cl
keeping travis.ci happy

implemented variable reflectivity

things look quite nice atm, I'd just like to implement some gaussian blurring
